          "markText": "货币的本质，并不是一种充当交易媒介的商品，而是一套可转让的信用记录体系。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1741653243,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-03-11 08:34:03",
          "chapterUid": 171,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=171&rangeStart=2878&rangeEnd=2914",
