        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 170,
      "chapterTitle": "自序 资本的历史进程",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "35781804_170_408-460",
          "range": "408-460",
          "rangeStart": 408,
          "rangeEnd": 460,
          "markText": "资金不等于资本。资金存在的主要目的是支付，或是一种价值储存和交换媒介。而资本的目的，是为了获取剩余价值。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1741653236,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-03-11 08:33:56",
          "chapterUid": 170,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=170&rangeStart=408&rangeEnd=460",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=170&rangeStart=408&rangeEnd=460"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_170_408-460",
      "chapterUid": 170,
      "range": "408-460",
      "markText": "资金不等于资本。资金存在的主要目的是支付，或是一种价值储存和交换媒介。而资本的目的，是为了获取剩余价值。",
      "totalCount": 1485,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=170&rangeStart=408&rangeEnd=460",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=170&rangeStart=408&rangeEnd=460"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_174_8698-8720",
      "chapterUid": 174,
      "range": "8698-8720",
      "markText": "人类的真正价值在于觉醒和思考，而不只是生存。",
      "totalCount": 1134,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=174&rangeStart=8698&rangeEnd=8720",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=174&rangeStart=8698&rangeEnd=8720"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_171_2878-2914",
      "chapterUid": 171,
      "range": "2878-2914",
      "markText": "货币的本质，并不是一种充当交易媒介的商品，而是一套可转让的信用记录体系。",
      "totalCount": 1078,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=171&rangeStart=2878&rangeEnd=2914",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=171&rangeStart=2878&rangeEnd=2914"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_171_505-551",
      "chapterUid": 171,
      "range": "505-551",
      "markText": "资本是人类对货币时间价值的一种利用和开发，目的是获取还不存在、属于想象中的未来物品——利润。",
      "totalCount": 840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=171&rangeStart=505&rangeEnd=551",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=171&rangeStart=505&rangeEnd=551"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_174_17580-17611",
      "chapterUid": 174,
      "range": "17580-17611",
      "markText": "许多罗马人过着醉生梦死的日子，不结婚，不生育，不履行父母责任。",
      "totalCount": 728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=174&rangeStart=17580&rangeEnd=17611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=174&rangeStart=17580&rangeEnd=17611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_174_13924-13999",
      "chapterUid": 174,
      "range": "13924-13999",
      "markText": "对于个人来说，解决债务危机的最好捷径是抢劫。 对于国家来说，解决债务危机的最佳办法是军事扩张。",
      "totalCount": 697,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=174&rangeStart=13924&rangeEnd=13999",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=174&rangeStart=13924&rangeEnd=13999"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_174_18477-18550",
      "chapterUid": 174,
      "range": "18477-18550",
      "markText": "当人们不再相信未来，人们就会去相信神，相信一切都是上帝的安排。 这是一个寂静、平衡的世界。",
      "totalCount": 688,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=174&rangeStart=18477&rangeEnd=18550",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=174&rangeStart=18477&rangeEnd=18550"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_170_1034-1059",
      "chapterUid": 170,
      "range": "1034-1059",
      "markText": "货币让人相信现在，而资本则建立在相信未来的基础上。",
      "totalCount": 680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=170&rangeStart=1034&rangeEnd=1059",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=170&rangeStart=1034&rangeEnd=1059"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_171_2092-2122",
      "chapterUid": 171,
      "range": "2092-2122",
      "markText": "这个合作秩序的本质，就是利益共享、风险共担，核心是“相信”。",
      "totalCount": 594,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=171&rangeStart=2092&rangeEnd=2122",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=171&rangeStart=2092&rangeEnd=2122"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_174_16086-16110",
      "chapterUid": 174,
      "range": "16086-16110",
      "markText": "罗马皇帝们最大的金融创新，就是往金属货币里掺假。",
      "totalCount": 578,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=174&rangeStart=16086&rangeEnd=16110",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=174&rangeStart=16086&rangeEnd=16110"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_171_9050-9081",
      "chapterUid": 171,
      "range": "9050-9081",
      "markText": "我们之所以如此固执地相信未来，是因为除此之外，再没有别的选项。",
      "totalCount": 576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=171&rangeStart=9050&rangeEnd=9081",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=171&rangeStart=9050&rangeEnd=9081"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_171_6953-7016",
      "chapterUid": 171,
      "range": "6953-7016",
      "markText": "任何资本都有一种狂想病，企图不用生产过程做媒介而直接获取利润。资本的过度积累常常增加市场泡沫，导致脱实向虚，失去资源配置功能。",
      "totalCount": 532,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=171&rangeStart=6953&rangeEnd=7016",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=171&rangeStart=6953&rangeEnd=7016"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_185_21525-21555",
      "chapterUid": 185,
      "range": "21525-21555",
      "markText": "那些嚷嚷着“不惜一切代价”的人，是因为他们不是那个“代价”！",
      "totalCount": 532,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=185&rangeStart=21525&rangeEnd=21555",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=185&rangeStart=21525&rangeEnd=21555"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_170_1935-1989",
      "chapterUid": 170,
      "range": "1935-1989",
      "markText": "资本秩序开始崛起，资本不但控制人的身体，也开始控制人的思想，最终超越宗教、国家，成为支配当代社会的重要因素。",
      "totalCount": 462,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=170&rangeStart=1935&rangeEnd=1989",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=170&rangeStart=1935&rangeEnd=1989"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35781804_170_700-784",
      "chapterUid": 170,
      "range": "700-784",
      "markText": "马克思在《资本论》中指出，“假如必须等待积累去使某些单个资本增长到能够修铁路的程度，那么恐怕直到今天世界上还没有铁路，但是，集中通过股份公司转瞬之间就把这件事完成了”。",
      "totalCount": 448,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35781804&chapterUid=170&rangeStart=700&rangeEnd=784",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c0332d807221fcacc0362ac?chapterUid=170&rangeStart=700&rangeEnd=784"
    },
    {
